Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def

This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBpelDefReader Interface for working with AeDef object readers.
IAeCopyOperationStrategyMatcher implements the matching logic for determining the strategy to use for a or def in a copy operation
IAeErrorReportingDefVisitor Simple extension to the def visitor interface to introduce error reporting capabilities.
IAeFromStrategyKeys The from strategies .
IAeFromStrategyNames Names for the from strategies
IAeReaderDefVisitor A reader def visitor is used by the dispatch reader to actually read the attributes of a def from the XML Element.
IAeReaderDefVisitorFactory A factory interface for creating reader def visitors.
IAeToStrategyKeys Sstrategies for selecting the "L" value in a copy operation.
IAeToStrategyNames Names of the strategies for selecting the "L" value in a copy operation
 

Class Summary
AeBaseDefReader Simple base class for AeDef object readers.
AeBPWSReaderVisitor A BPEL4WS 1.1 implementation of a reader visitor.
AeCommonSpecStrategyMatcher Creates specs or prototype objects for the commmon and variants and maps them to the strategy names.
AeCommonSpecStrategyMatcher.AeBaseVarSpec Base class for the specs, provides base impl of a spec matcher along with constants and a BitSet to record which values are enabled in the from or to def.
AeCommonSpecStrategyMatcher.AeFromSpec Extension to the base spec that adds specs for the AeFromDef;
AeCommonSpecStrategyMatcher.AeToSpec Creates a spec for the given spec
AeDispatchReader Generic AeBaseDefReader impl that creates a new instance of its child class and uses double dispatch to populate it based on type.
AeExpressionSpecStrategyKey An extension of the basic spec strategy key, this version represents a strategy that is dynamically generated by the matcher when the to-spec is a 'expression' form.
AeReaderVisitor Responsible for setting all of the properties on the newly created AeDef objects from the current xml element and adding then def to their parent def.
AeSpecStrategyKey A simple key that is used to indicate the strategy to use for the To portion of a copy operation.
AeWSBPELAbstractProcessReaderVisitor Implements a WS-BPEL 2.0 abstract process version of the def reader visitor.
AeWSBPELReaderVisitor Implements a WS-BPEL 2.0 version of the def reader visitor.
AeWSBPELSpecStrategyMatcher Impl of the strategy matcher that adds additional patterns for WS-BPEL
